title: #92Noon Live from TCO! Wobby/Russo/Wiggins/Lombardi/Zimmer & Belichick Pressers
description: 92Noon is back at the TCO Performance Center as the Vikings prepare to battle the Patriots in Foxboro! Wobby stops by to preview the matchup, The Athletic's Michael Russo talks about a disappointing Minnesota Wild loss in an emergecy Russo Radio, Mike Zimmer holds his weekly presser, Nordo and PA go through some of Patriots Head Coach Bill Belichick's press conference call, the Birk Bit makes his regular appearance, former Viking and Patriot Jermaine Wiggins gives some insight on the Patriots, and Matt Lombardi calls in to talk all things football!
